    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>cooked beef strips</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further or until warmed through – this is your <strong>beef rendang</strong></p><p>Fluff the <strong>green bean rice</strong> with a fork</p>",
      "order": 7,
